parameters: \n< Suspicious Tool Shop >...There's not much of anything special, you know.

\n< Suspicious Tool Shop >Welcome. Oh my, what brings a young lady like
yourself to our store?

\n< Serena >I wasn't asked by anyone. It's... something...
special, you could say. Anyway, I came here to
deliver a package...

\n< Suspicious Tool Shop >Ah, you must be the one. Yes, we have it in stock
at our store. Please, hand it over.

\n< Suspicious Tool Shop >Oh my, oh my. This is quite a chubby little baby.
Yes, yes, it already has teeth too. These claws
look like they could yield something good.

\n< Suspicious Tool Shop >The eyeballs have a beautiful shape. The skull
shape is also good, with a wide occipital region.
The quality of the mother's body must have been
good.

\n< Serena >Um... There's something off about this... What
will happen to this child? What do you plan to do?

\n< Suspicious Tool Shop >The uses for goblin and monster babies... There's
only one, right?

\n< Suspicious Tool Shop >...Ah! Of course, a human baby would be
preferable, right? However, that's not possible
here. It would be troublesome, you see. After all,
the city wouldn't stay silent about it.

\n< Suspicious Tool Shop >Yes, for our store, monster babies are sufficient.
We can meet the demand, yes.

\n< Suspicious Tool Shop >So, if you could bring us a freshly born, still
alive, high- quality one like this, it would be
really helpful.

\n< Suspicious Tool Shop >We have a mutually beneficial relationship with
adventurers. I hope you will also become a patron
at this opportunity.
\n< Suspicious Tool Shop >So, as a return, take this.

\n< Suspicious Tool Shop >Compared to those derived from magic, the
effectiveness is slightly inferior, you know.

\n< Serena >Potion... I wonder if it has any effect on
physical condition...? If I bring this back and
make her drink it, maybe that woman will calm down
a little.

\n< Suspicious Tool Shop >If you ever find yourself in need of a monster
baby, please come visit us. Instead of cash, we
will provide you with a special item as
compensation.
\n< Serena >I don't think I'll ever come here again...
\n< Serena >...Let's go back to the guild for now.

\n< Suspicious Tool Shop >Welcome to the Magic Tool Shop. We are not
inferior to the regular tool shops on the main
street in terms of practicality.
Oh, customer. What brings you here today?
I want you to adopt a monster child
Please adopt a child of a monster.

\n< Suspicious Tool Shop >Oh my, oh my. This is troublesome. We specialize
in monster children here. We do not handle human
children.
I guess i'll quit after all
\n< Suspicious Tool Shop >I see. Well then, until next time.

\n< Suspicious Tool Shop >Oh, this is a Stalion baby. Oh, I see, I've seen
something rare.
\n< Suspicious Tool Shop >Is this for customers to give birth?

\n< Suspicious Tool Shop >Well, to be able to give birth with such a small
body. In other words, surviving the mating with
that creature... Ah, my apologies.

\n< Suspicious Tool Shop >Anyway, thank you for this valuable item. I must
show my gratitude as well.

\n< Suspicious Tool Shop >Here, we have a particularly effective spiritual
medicine and...
\n< Suspicious Tool Shop >And this may be unnecessary, but vaginal ointment.

\n< Suspicious Tool Shop >This ointment here has the effect of caring for
the female genitalia. In other words, well... it
can restore the condition. It's only a little bit
though.

\n< Suspicious Tool Shop >We also have another ointment for the anus, so if
you need it, please feel free to ask anytime.
I don't have any particular business
\n< Suspicious Tool Shop >I see. Well then, until next time.

\n< Andre >Well, well, Serena-san, do you need something?

\n< Serena >......I'm troubled because I've been parasitized
by a slime. I'm sorry, but could you give me some
medicine?

\n< Andre >Haha, a slime from the sewer, huh? Yes, of course,
that's fine. However, I'm sorry, but could you
please bring me some slime in this bottle?

\n< Andre >You seem to be in pain. However, I am not involved
in charity work... What would you like me to do?

\n< Serena >......I understand. I understand, so please give
me that medicine.

\n< Andre >Negotiations have been successful. The restroom is
located in the back, so please feel free to use
it.

\n< Serena >(...In this, this despicable way... I am... even
worse than the man I caught...)
\n< Andre >So this is the infamous slime... Hmmm.

\n< Serena >D-Don't stare at it so much... It came out of my
body, you know.

\n< Andre >Oops, my apologies... However, I must admit that I
have done this many times before, looking at
things that came out of Serena's body.

\n< Andre >Ah, I apologize once again. Well then, this will
be the slime expulsion. It will involve expelling
the slime from your body all at once, so please
use a safe place.

\n< Andre >If it's alright with you, please bring the slime
again.
